title: Miller Zeit 12/19: Tulsi Gabbard, Democratic Debate, Kim Kardashian, James Wiseman, Tenet
itunes:title: Miller Zeit 12/19: Tulsi Gabbard, Democratic Debate, Kim Kardashian, James Wiseman, Tenet
description:
On this episode of Miller Zeit Jack is joined by Anna Hossnieh and Caitlin Durante to discuss Tulsi Gabbard voting "present", the Dem Debate happening tonight at LMU, Kim K photoshopped North into their family Holiday pictures, James Wiseman drafting fiasco, and the new Christopher Nolan film 'Tenet'.
